Mabel Makun sings a birthday song as she celebrates her husband, Ayo Makun popularly known as AY on his 48th birthday. Gistvic Reports. “You Are Multi-talented ” – Mabel Makun Sings To Celebrate Her Husband, AY On His 48th Birthday (VIDEO) She wrote: “You are brave You are smart You are intelligent You are multitalented You are very hardworking You have defied all odds to get to where you are today You are my lover,husband and friend You are Ayodeji Gboyegami Richard Makun. Happy birthday @aycomedian ❤️❤️😍😍May God continue to keep you in good health,long life and more blessings. Loads of love from wifey 🤪🤪”